content:
I dunno, 36 perks still feel like a lot. I do like RPGs that don't allow you to get everything at once and require you to plan your build out but I have a feeling with the 36 points you're gonna be skimming really close to having everything.

&#x200B;

Unless these talents have more than one rank, that'd be the only way I'm content with the talent system for this game.
